# MERN Sports Platform API Tests
# Use VS Code REST Client extension to run these

### Health Check
GET http://localhost:5000/api/health

### MongoDB Connection Test
GET http://localhost:5000/api/db-test

### API Info
GET http://localhost:5000/api

### Database Statistics (Users, Fields, Bookings count)
GET http://localhost:5000/api/stats

### All Users (see who logged in)
GET http://localhost:5000/api/users

### All Fields (see available sports fields)
GET http://localhost:5000/api/fields

### All Bookings (see field reservations)
GET http://localhost:5000/api/bookings

### Database Collections Info
GET http://localhost:5000/api/collections

